="width: 3963px; left: -1px;">Zayn Sabri - Hi guys, if 4wd any new and unattended cases of landslides or trees falling over their houses, or their houses are deemed unsafe overflow by the current weather situation in brunei muara area pls contact 2380804 or inbox me with full name, contact no and an accurate address. Your cooperation by giving us the accurate and valid details will be much appreciated. We at the District Disaster Management Centre will try our very  to cater to every distress calls made. May Allah grant us patience to go through this calamities.</div></td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="43458477R241" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">242</div></th><td class="s0">26/1/2014</td><td class="s2">Reaching people in need</td></tr><tr style='height:59px;'><th id="43458477R242" style="height: 59px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 59px;">243</div></th><td class="s0">26/1/2014</td><td class="s3">Deep floods along F19 leading towards Lg 14. Drive safely, peeps... Depressing weather....<br>at Asset Engineering &amp; Projects Services, K-Block, Panaga<br>pic credit: Rosie Abdullah</td></tr><tr style='height:159px;'><th id="43458477R243" style="height: 159px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 159px;">244</div></th><td class="s0">26/1/2014</td><td class="s3">Aziz Mohamad TheBuzer via Flooding Brunei<br><br>For it to be a volunteer or in charge and , prepare yourselves , be fit and healthy body , to dress bright, light and if possible use a reflector vest or life- jacket . Wear hardy shoes . 1st priority is their own health before helping others .. do preventive vaccination <br><br><br>Health officials advise to us before starting the task<br><br>Prepare your mental, because we will hear anything from publics, which are good and some ar