ransportation.<br><br>O , all things are subjected us to help flood victims at this time. I hope everything goes well. And you shall be strong through all their hearts that this allegation and hopefully they will be more patient and calm in what they&#39;ve been through this. Hopefully Brunei Darussalam and all its people will always be in your protection. Amin Ya Allah, Ya Rahman Amin, Amin ya Rahim.<br><br>Lillahhi Taala. Allahhuakbar.</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="43458477R246" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">247</div></th><td class="s0">26/1/2014</td><td class="s2">The weather was quite cold today . In some places there is still rain . Watch out people.</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="43458477R247" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">248</div></th><td class="s0">27/1/2014</td><td class="s2">picture taken on 20th january 2014, crocodile could be seen behind our house</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="43458477R248" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">249</div></th><td class="s0">27/1/2014</td><td class="s2">is that a crocodile?</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="43458477R249" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">250</div></th><td class="s0">27/1/2014</td><td class="s2">yess crocodile</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="43458477R250" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">251</div></th><td class="s0">27/1/2014</td><td class="s2">hope avoided of  bad disaster</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="43458477R251" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-hea